Identify commonalities and differences between Publication, Book and
Magazine classes. Title, Price, Copies are common instance variables and
saleCopy is common method. The differences are, Bookclass has author and
order Copies(). Magazine Class has orderQty, Currentissue, reciveissue().Write
a program to find how many copies of the given books are ordered and display
total sale of publication.





import java.util.Scanner;
